{"tid":1748122,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"區議會選舉「必勝」功略","createTime":"2019-11-23T13:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T14:43:52.000Z","uid":316224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5bfc9f8f98a1a600c6b5ead9a8c958cde55db91f","tid":1748122,"uid":316224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:46:06.000Z","msg":"民意調查好明顯知道7成人係黃<br />\n每次遊行都係我方人數多過對方好多<br />\n你知 我知 大家都知道！<br />\n<br />\n區選如果......<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">非建制贏：顯示真民意！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">建制贏：種票，北京操作選舉！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n講大家準備好唔同情況下 我地要宣揚嘅信息！<br />\n區選如期進行，係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公我贏，字你輸</span></span>局面<br />\n<br />\n第二樣嘢，<br />\n建制派一直都有大數據，識得分配唔同票數到唔同地方，以達至贏到更多席位。<br />\n例如：A區，有1000票係投建制嘅，但佢用大數據計算後只需要800票就會贏到，咁佢就會拎多咗個200票去第2區作選民。所以我地喺連登，或者其他好多渠道都睇到有種票跡象。<br />\n所以，最後我哋可能會輸！<br />\n但係，真正要睇嘅，<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">未必係贏幾多席，<br />\n而係471區加埋支持非建制嘅人數總數係咪較多！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家聽日可以去投票<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095c19a9d25e22d1279634f6911fe1da2660659e","tid":1748122,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"香城online玩家大型活動 投票Challenge<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"22135f09255ce1e8b019382c712e59e5c9e0de09","tid":1748122,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8yQUK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8yQUK2.png&h=727d0b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等候時及面對<span style=\"color: red;\">白警</span>時唱<strong>《Sing Hallelujah To The Lord》</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港區 6:00pm 灣仔紅隧入口集合，大量兩層巴士接過紅隧，或自行行過紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【急】請傳給撞區候選人！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n必在 11月 24日 7:30am 前，在facebook發表，證明已為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7－11pm</span></strong>活動申請不反通知書，先發表就出線有票，遲發表要退選。</span><br />\n撞區表 <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Fp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=04951e1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、所有民主派議員、及候選人。〔民主派即是所有推動民主，包括本土及泛民〕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫幫手推一推行動post拉！連登重有邊個唔去投票！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】"}]}